name: XSOAR Check APIs
description: This custom content pack XSOAR 8 Migration - API Endpoints Check allows XSOAR Administrators to identify API endpoints in use within Automations and Integrations. It does this by collecting a content bundle and parsing out automations and integrations that make use of **`core-api-*`** or **`demisto-api-*`** calls in the code.
author: Abel S. Santamarina
